body_html: @fcalvet I'm not sure how our uploader broke this badly on Windows. It indeed uploaded to the soumith channel rather than pytorch. We've uploaded the packages to pytorch now and are fixing the script. Thanks a ton for reporting.

body: @fcalvet I'm not sure how our uploader broke this badly on Windows. It indeed uploaded to the `soumith` channel rather than `pytorch`. We've uploaded the packages to `pytorch` now and are fixing the script. Thanks a ton for reporting.
